# GoGPIO

Nothing special about this repository, I am experimenting with GPIO on an ESP32
device.

## Setup

### Install tinyGo

https://tinygo.org/getting-started/install/macos/

```
brew tap tinygo-org/tools
brew install tinygo
```

### Install ESP Toolkit

**This worked for me, YMMV\***

https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/release-v3.0/get-started/linux-setup.html#standard-setup-of-toolchain-for-linux

https://dl.espressif.com/dl/xtensa-esp32-elf-osx-1.22.0-80-g6c4433a-5.2.0.tar.gz

### Install the blink app

tinygo flash -target=esp32-wroom-32 -port=/dev/ttyUSB0 blink.go
